snippet.title: A Measurement of the Kinetic Sunyaev-Zel'dovich Signal Toward MACS J0717.5+3745
snippet.description: A Measurement of the Kinetic Sunyaev-Zel'dovich Signal Toward MACS J0717.5+3745 / Sayers, Jack ; Mroczkowski, Tony ; Zemcov, Michael ; Korngut, Phil M ; Bock, James ; Bulbul, Esra ; Czakon, Nicole G ; Egami, Eiichi ; Golwala, Sunil R ; Koch, Patrick M et al. We report our analysis of MACS J0717.5+3745 using 140 and 268 GHz Bolocam data collected at the Caltech Submillimeter Observatory. We detect extended Sunyaev-Zel'dovich (SZ) effect signal at high significance in both Bolocam bands, and we employ Herschel-SPIRE observations to subtract the signal from dusty background galaxies in the 268 GHz data. snippet.description: Search for long-lived stopped R-hadrons decaying out-of-time with pp collisions using the ATLAS detector / ATLAS Collaboration An updated search is performed for gluino, top squark, or bottom squark R-hadrons that have come to rest within the ATLAS calorimeter, and decay at some later time to hadronic jets and a neutralino, using 5.0 and 22.9 fb$^{-1}$ of pp collisions at 7 and 8 TeV, respectively. Candidate decay events are triggered in selected empty bunch crossings of the LHC in order to remove pp collision backgrounds.
